{"tid":1029604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大擬於下學年開辦5年制自資護理學課程　正待護士管理局審批","createTime":"2019-02-20T11:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T18:42:10.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2eea5053221db804383b5ed7271fa702ce5b92c6","tid":1029604,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/297401/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E6%93%AC%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%8B%E5%AD%B8%E5%B9%B4%E9%96%8B%E8%BE%A65%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%87%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E5%AD%B8%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%80%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F297401%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25BE%25A65%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%2589%25B9&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n83hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=e81a463e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/297401/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E6%93%AC%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%8B%E5%AD%B8%E5%B9%B4%E9%96%8B%E8%BE%A65%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B6%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%87%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E5%AD%B8%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%80%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9</a><br />\n冬季流感在過去數月肆虐香港，導致公立醫院壓力負荷過重，醫護人手短缺問題再次浮現。香港浸會大學今日（20日）與傳媒茶聚時宣布，校方正籌備開辦5年制護理學學士自資課程，目前正接受護士管理局評審，期望最快可於下學年正式開辦。<br />\n浸大持續教育學院院長鍾志杰表示，鑒於本港近年護士人手短缺，校方去年已聘請數名具備博士學歷的資深護理人員，並已成立「護理教育部」，籌備開辦護理學學士自資課程。他表示，目前課程正處於護士管理局評審最後階段，有信心課程能順利獲批，期望可於下學年正式開辦。<br />\n<br />\n課程已處於護士管理局評審最後階段<br />\n<br />\n至於招生人數、學費等細節方面，鍾志杰由於課程仍在評審階段，目前未能確認相關資料。惟他補充，目前指定專業／界別課程資助計劃（SSSDP）涵蓋部分自資院校的護理系課程，而教資會資助院校的自資課程一般不包括在內。<br />\n<br />\n另外，浸大計劃於明年開辦6個新本科課程，包括：創意產業音樂學士、生物資源與農業科學理學士（JS2510理學士課程其中一項主修）、地理／歷史／社會學及個人、社會及人文教學（雙學位課程）、商業計算及數據分析理學士，以及與西門費莎大學合辦的工商管理學學士雙學位課程、數學及統計理學士及精算理學士雙學位課程。"},{"pid":"27645a3febc67f3bbf12afcb88444e1142578021","tid":1029604,"uid":25221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6230f3a3e5f7083df50e2a52266bb6454255cda","tid":1029604,"uid":61630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd1f8acfb8246b00df52b6ce70eb7553cb271d2","tid":1029604,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"浸會醫院係正隔離<br />\n實習就去個度?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3269b8a6949ab33bcb85de0bca64680b071c216d","tid":1029604,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"為大灣區居民服務 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617387052400950e9456d41b57c297c21e420a38","tid":1029604,"uid":51469,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f6230f3a3e5f7083df50e2a52266bb6454255cda","tid":1029604,"uid":61630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"有排都唔爆掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708d808307ab9fe3ae6a186f35be931f79983338","tid":1029604,"uid":211579,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"Campus 細撚到仆街啦已經，common area 又少，做劏房生意咩，仲要開周街都有得讀嘅nursing 做乜春呀，屌你老母"},{"pid":"10e218d45daaeb93f43c3769889e10e374b8562e","tid":1029604,"uid":65201,"like":0,"disl